{
  "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.35,
      "size": 37584,
      "text": "这是一片数学画出来的雪花，边缘越看越细，怎么放大都有花边。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.17,
      "size": 34704,
      "text": "它有个古怪的名字，叫科赫雪花，藏着一个让人吃惊的秘密。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.19,
      "size": 34992,
      "text": "别急，我们从一个普通的等边三角形开始，一步步把它变成雪花。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "rule-1",
      "filename": "rule-rule-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/rule-rule-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "规则很简单：把每条边平均分成三段。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "rule-2",
      "filename": "rule-rule-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/rule-rule-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.19,
      "size": 34992,
      "text": "去掉中间那一段，换上一个向外凸的等边三角形的另外两条边。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "rule-3",
      "filename": "rule-rule-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/rule-rule-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.1,
      "size": 33552,
      "text": "于是原来的一条线段，就变成了折出尖角的四条线段。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "perimeter",
      "line_id": "peri-1",
      "filename": "perimeter-peri-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/perimeter-peri-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.3,
      "size": 36864,
      "text": "每迭代一次，边数变成四倍，而每条边长只剩三分之一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "perimeter",
      "line_id": "peri-3",
      "filename": "perimeter-peri-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/perimeter-peri-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.62,
      "size": 41904,
      "text": "一直迭代下去，周长按四比三的比例越涨越大，最终冲向无穷。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "area",
      "line_id": "area-2",
      "filename": "area-area-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/area-area-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.23,
      "size": 35712,
      "text": "每次新增的小三角越来越小，把它们加起来是一个收敛的等比级数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36720,
      "text": "调整迭代层数，看雪花的边缘怎样一层层长出更细的花边。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.17,
      "size": 34704,
      "text": "留意右侧数值：周长不停变大，面积却几乎纹丝不动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "科赫雪花用一条简单规则，折出无限精细的自相似边缘。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "无穷的周长包住有限的面积，这正是分形最迷人的地方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.2,
      "size": 35136,
      "text": "有限里藏着无限，愿你继续探索数学之美，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
